OL,7,FConsumer trust in water companies
OL,8,Frisks being "irreversibly damaged"
OL,9,Funless they see a sustained
OL,10,Fimprovement in the sector's care of
OL,11,Fthe environment, an annual survey has
OL,12,Ffound.
OL,14,FHousehold satisfaction with water
OL,15,Fcompanies across all measures has seen
OL,16,Fan unprecedented decline, the Consumer
OL,17,FCouncil for Water found.
