OL,3,C'Unprecedented' fall in water firm
OL,4,Ccustomer satisfaction amid pollution
OL,5,Cfailings
OL,7,FThe survey of almost 5,000 households,
OL,8,Fwhich has been taken for 13 years,
OL,9,Frecorded the starkest decline in
OL,10,Fcustomer satisfaction with how
OL,11,Fcompanies clean and manage wastewater
OL,12,Fbefore its release back into the
OL,13,Fenvironment. Just 35% were satisfied
OL,14,Fwith this, compared to 88% a decade
OL,15,Fago.
OL,17,FSatisfaction with companies' efforts
OL,18,Fto minimise sewer flooding has also
OL,19,Fplummeted over the same period,
OL,20,Ffalling to 43% compared to 85% in 2014.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G2/9
