OL,3,C'Unprecedented' fall in water firm
OL,4,Ccustomer satisfaction amid pollution
OL,5,Cfailings
OL,7,FJust half of households agreed their
OL,8,Fcompany cared about the service it
OL,9,Fprovided, also down 14%, while 55%
OL,10,Ffelt what they were being charged for
OL,11,Fservices was fair, down 9% from last
OL,12,Fyear to its lowest ever level.
OL,14,FTrust in water companies also reached
OL,15,Fits lowest level ` a score of 6.37 out
OL,16,Fof 10 ` since the survey began. Every
OL,17,Fwater company saw its trust score
OL,18,Ffall, with energy suppliers overtaking
OL,19,Fwater for the first time as a more
OL,20,Ftrusted utility across England and
OL,21,FWales.
