OL,3,C'Unprecedented' fall in water firm
OL,4,Ccustomer satisfaction amid pollution
OL,5,Cfailings
OL,7,FCompanies in the south east of England
OL,8,Fgenerally fared worse but the picture
OL,9,Felsewhere ` particularly on
OL,10,Fenvironmental matters ` remained
OL,11,Fbroadly negative.
OL,13,FThe findings come just weeks before
OL,14,Fregulator Ofwat publishes its draft
OL,15,Fdeterminations on what water companies
OL,16,Fin England and Wales can charge
OL,17,Fcustomers over the next five years,
OL,18,Fwith bills expected to rise
OL,19,Fsignificantly over the period.
