OL,3,C'Unprecedented' fall in water firm
OL,4,Ccustomer satisfaction amid pollution
OL,5,Cfailings
OL,7,FCCW chief executive Mike Keil said:
OL,8,F"These are the worst results we've
OL,9,Fever seen in our survey and it largely
OL,10,Fstems from customers' concerns over
OL,11,Fcompanies' environmental performance.
OL,12,FIt's little surprise people are
OL,13,Fquestioning whether they are getting a
OL,14,Ffair deal.
