OL,4,Ccustomer satisfaction amid pollution
OL,5,Cfailings
OL,7,F"Trust won't be rebuilt and customers
OL,8,Fwill not tolerate future bill rises
OL,9,Funless they see and feel a step change
OL,10,Fin the service they receive from their
OL,11,Fwater company ` whether that's having
OL,12,Fthe confidence to swim at their local
OL,13,Fbeach or experiencing a more reliable
OL,14,Fwater supply. If customers are going
OL,15,Fto be asked to pay considerably more,
OL,16,Fthey have a right to expect far more
OL,17,Fin return."
